snippet.title: Grand Theft Auto V -- Coming for PlayStation 4 this Fall | E3 2014
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/grand-theft-auto-v/?emcid=or-1s-412983

The critically-acclaimed and record-breaking Grand Theft Auto V comes to a new generation this Fall. 

Grand Theft Auto V for PlayStation 4 will take full advantage of the power of new generation system to deliver the ultimate open-world experience. 

Pre-order now and visit http://www.rockstargames.com/V for more details.
